Use unison to sync between mac and ubuntu

use this link to install unison on headless ubuntu

https://eric.blog/2017/08/25/how-to-install-unison-2-48-on-ubuntu/#comment-32309


To install in mac : brew install unison

Documentation is in https://www.cis.upenn.edu/~bcpierce/unison/download/releases/stable/unison-manual.html

quick way to run is

unison -auto <source dir in local machine> ssh://root@<destination IP>/<destination dir name> &
